                <p>During the Xbox Developer Direct January 2025, Koei Tecmo surprised-dropped Ninja Gaiden 2 Black for PC, PlayStation, and Xbox. The game is also available on Xbox Game Pass.</p><p>This is a remaster of the 2008 game and is described as the definitive way to play. "We also wanted to give players something to enjoy as they wait for the release of Ninja Gaiden 4," said producer Fumihiko Yasuda, in an <a href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2025/01/23/ninja-gaiden-4-developer-direct-2025/" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">interview with Xbox</a>. "We chose Ninja Gaiden 2 because it stands as one of the most solid action games in the series."</p>



    
